  "text": "The input samples fed to the P-GWR network are concatenations of the temporally ordered BMUs from the preceding layer [CITATION_1] . We divide the input into two parts: 1) the regressor, x in (t) and 2) the desired output, i.e., the value to predict x out (t)",
